description:
Superior Iron Man Volume 1

An Avengers Now! series in the spirit of Superior Spider-Man. Continued from Iron Man Vol.5 and the events of Avengers & X-Men: Axis, comes a new, superior Iron Man. Tony, being inverted, sets foot on San Fransico! The series lasted for only 9 issues due to the events of Secret Wars in which Tony was reverted back to his old self. After Secret Wars, the series was continued into Invincible Iron Man Vol.2, the first series of the All-New All-Different Marvel line.

Collected Editions

  • Superior Iron Man: Infamous (#1-5)
name: Superior Iron Man
